      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The exterior has noticeable rust on the wheel wells and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear including tears in the upholstery and a non-functional head unit. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and there is a persistent leak in the transmission system; it is recommended that the buyer tows the vehicle. This is a project car best suited for parts or a complete overhaul.",
