    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly superlative condition. This meticulously curated example remains in showroom-quality state, featuring a flawless finish and an interior that retains its original luster. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the highest standards of automotive excellence. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection without compromise, this vehicle offers an unrivaled driving experience and lasting value.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m putting my absolute pride and joy up for sale, and honestly, it breaks my heart a little to let her go. This beauty has been pampered since day one\u2014always kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single weekend. She looks and feels like she just rolled off the showroom floor. The paint is deep and glossy, and the interior still has that fresh smell. You might find a microscopic speck here or there if you\u2019re looking with a magnifying glass, but she\u2019s as close to perfect as you can get. I\u2019ve handled all the maintenance early, so she runs like a dream. Come on by, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered for the serious collector: A superlative E92 M3 in concours-ready condition. This S65 V8 has been fastidiously maintained with a proactive mechanical refresh, including treated rod bearing replacement and uprated throttle actuators to future-proof the drivetrain. The subframe has been bore-scoped and confirmed defect-free, while the suspension retains its factory-fresh damping profile. Fluid analysis reports show zero metallic deviation, and the DCT features the GTS software flash for optimized clamping force and lightning-quick engagement. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, recently treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating. This is a mechanically sorted, turn-key masterpiece for the driver who demands peak performance without the typical ownership liabilities.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Showroom condition. Zero flaws. Mechanically perfect. Best price on the market. Won't last.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule where every stitch of leather tells a story of elegance and every turn of the key is a promise of adventure. This isn't just a machine; it\u2019s a masterwork preserved in its purest form, a whisper of automotive perfection that glides through the world with effortless grace. Its silhouette catches the golden hour glow like a dream you never want to wake from. To drive it is to command a symphony of engineering, a rare opportunity to own a piece of history that remains as vibrant and stirring as the day it first touched the asphalt.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade vehicle in true showroom condition. This specimen has been meticulously preserved, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in an as-new state. Every detail, from the factory-perfect paint depth to the pristine mechanical components, reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the pre-owned market. This is not merely a vehicle; it is a definitive example of the model, offering unparalleled quality for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection. Fully inspected and ready for the most rigorous evaluation.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the joy it brings. This car is in absolute showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since the day I brought it home, keeping it tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washing it every single weekend. It drives like it just rolled off the lot and looks even better in person. You won't find a cleaner example in the neighborhood. Come on by, let's chat cars, and I'll show you why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a turn-key masterpiece for the discerning pilot. This chassis has been meticulously curated with a focus on rotational mass reduction and thermal efficiency. Featuring a bespoke Stage 2 re-map optimized for 93 octane, the powerband is exceptionally linear with virtually zero transient lag. The suspension geometry has been precision-aligned to eliminate bump steer, while the drivetrain exhibits zero lash thanks to upgraded high-durometer bushings. Every fluid circuit has been cycled with high-temp synthetics, and recent compression testing shows all cylinders within a 2% variance\u2014factory spec or better. This isn't just a vehicle; it's a mechanically synchronized extension of the driver. 'Mint' is an understatement for this level of structural integrity and aesthetic preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
